  "text": "Swift Trust [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Occurs when individuals decide to trust others prior to developing longer term relationships. Swift trust develops as a function of members' own dispositional tendencies, quickly discernable surface-level cues of others, and imported trust-related information.",
